{"tid":59886,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一post塞爆連登系列]召集當年屋企有SEGA家用機既巴打","createTime":"2016-12-30T04:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T15:38:14.000Z","uid":15410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d4cf8f299d77363fee9fb58419374fcac16d74","tid":59886,"uid":15410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"數吓呢度有幾多細個玩sega機既少數族裔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學個陣屋企有親戚俾既白色sega saturn。記得細個最鐘意玩saturn隻3D彈珠人、sega賽車(好似係)，同埋可以同屋企人鳩玩既人生遊戲，雖然全家唔識日文一舖可以打足一晚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外親戚送既碟仲有埋櫻花大戰，但小學雞加上冇save卡當年玩唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n差唔多2008之後轉玩nds同online game先入返主流，到而家睇開家用機歷史，發現當年日本sega連啲自嘲廣告都好高質。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無sega fans分享吓當年你用邊部機玩開咩game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">而家大個玩pso2養女又係好撚好玩</span>"},{"pid":"911de65d016341bd0f2e3b7beabb0b7447e92aca","tid":59886,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"世家五代<br />\n<br />\nBare knuckle 1 2 3 都好J到爆<br />\n<br />\n仲有幽遊四打<br />\n<br />\n超音鼠"},{"pid":"debde8b81da5451232d6990b0161eeec6c1c2150","tid":59886,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:47:13.000Z","msg":"Saturn 就打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.gamefaqs.net/box/9/0/0/35900_front.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.gamefaqs.net%2Fbox%2F9%2F0%2F0%2F35900_front.jpg&h=4d7fcbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係好J到暈"},{"pid":"2c00619c6b681cc158bf9c74734bbafaad7e8603","tid":59886,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"Saturn 以前有d咸game都日日玩"},{"pid":"664ef30808723a6573ea8db498fbd57f5235efee","tid":59886,"uid":15410,"like"